content:
## CSS Animations

Animations are declared in two parts, definition and assignment


### Keyframe Definition

```css 
/* Assign Particular Action */ 

@keyframes animateModal {
    from {
        top: -300px;
        opacity: 0;
    }

    to {
        top: 50%;
        opacity: 1;
    }
}
```




### Keyframe Assignment

```css
/* Assign to Target Class  */ 
#modal {
    animation-name: animateModal;
    animation-duration: .4s;
}
```
